.⠀⠀
Oh, and since we’re stuck at home during the circuit breaker period, the second best thing you can do for her is to surprise her with this handwoven IKAT stole she will care deeply for. ⠀⠀
.⠀⠀
.⠀⠀
⠀⠀
All stoles are dyed in natural hues of the white, red, blue and grey. A perfect piece to brighten up any basic outfit look. ⠀⠀

Send us your personalised message for her and we will delivery it to her doorstep. ( In Singapore) ⠀⠀
